Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你看清楚怎么做了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You see how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}是啊 我想我找到窍门了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, I think I got the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:25.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你最好能行 如果把冰芯搞砸了老板会把我的脑袋拧下来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You better. The boss will chew my head off if these cores get messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}别担心\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们钻到二十六英尺深了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're at 26 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你让詹森一个人去操作钻探机？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You let Jason operate the drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嗯 他能行的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, he can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我什么都没做\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}把你的手伸给我！ 别管钻探机了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Give me your hand! Let go of the drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:00.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}别管了 杰克！ 太晚了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Forget it, Jack! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你办不到的！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克！ 把你的手给我！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack! Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我抓到你了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你刚才在想什么呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:56.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 这是怎么回事？- 整个冰架裂开了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- What's happening? - The whole damn shelf is breaking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}就是这样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That's what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们发现了一万年前灾难性的气候迁移的证据\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We found evidence of a cataclysmic climate shift, which occurred 10,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:23.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}{\fs14\bord0\shad3\b1}{\fsp1}{\pos(192,236)}{\fad(800,800)}新德里 联合国全球气候变暖会议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这些温室效应气体在冰芯中的聚集...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The concentration of these natural greenhouse gases in the ice cores...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}显示出气候失控性的变暖把地球推向冰川时代...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...indicates that runaway warming pushed Earth into an ice age...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}而这一直持续了两个世纪\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...which lasted two centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我被你搞糊涂了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我还以为你是在讨论全球变暖问题而不是冰川时代\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I thought you were talking about global warming, not an ice age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:47.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}是 有点自相矛盾 但全球变暖能导致气候冷却趋势 我来解释\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yes, it is a paradox, but global warming can trigger a cooling trend. Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:53.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}北大西洋暖流直接影响北半球气候\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The Northern Hemisphere owes its climate to the North Atlantic Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:57.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来自太阳的热量到达赤道后再由洋流传送到北方\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Heat from the sun arrives at the equator and is carried north by the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:03.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是全球变暖正在融化极地的冰川 而这干扰了这个洋流\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}But global warming is melting the polar ice caps and disrupting this flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:07.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}最后它会慢慢停下来 到那时候...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Eventually it will shut down. And when that occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们温暖的天气就消失了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...there goes our warm climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:15.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起 你认为这情形什么时候会发生呢？教授？什么时候？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Excuse me. When do you think this could happen, professor? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:19.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不知道 也许一百年 也许一千年 但是我知道...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I don't know. Maybe in 100 years, maybe in 1,000. But what I do know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:24.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果我们不很快采取行动 我们的子孙后代会为此付出代价\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...that if we do not act soon, our children and grandchildren will have to pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那谁将会为京都协定书付出代价呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And who's going to pay the price of the Kyoto Accord?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}世界经济将会为此损失亿万美元\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It would cost the world's economy hundreds of billions of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:39.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}恕我直言 副总统 如果现在我们不采取行动付出的代价会更高\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}With all due respect, Mr. Vice President, the cost of doing nothing could be even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们的气候十分脆弱\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Our climate is fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}按照我们燃烧原油和污染环境的速度...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}At the rate we're burning fossil fuels and polluting the environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}冰川将会很快消失\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...the ice caps will soon disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}霍尔教授\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Professor Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们的经济就象环境一样脆弱\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...our economy is every bit as fragile as the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:58.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许在做出这种耸人听闻的声明之前 你应该记住这一点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Perhaps you should keep that in mind before making sensationalist claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 上次断裂的冰块...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, the last chunk of ice that broke off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}差不多象罗德岛州那么大\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...was about the size of Rhode Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有些人可能会觉得这相当的耸人听闻\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Some people might call that pretty sensational.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}阻止全球变暖！阻止全球变暖！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Stop global warming! Stop global warming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我现在正在新德里的全球变暖会议场外\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm at the Global Warming Conference in New Delhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这里 难以置信的是 正在下雪\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...where, if you can believe it, it's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有史以来最寒冷的气候给整个城市造成了严重的混乱\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The coldest weather on record has thrown the city into chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}大量的无家可归者被冻死\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...with numbers of homeless people freezing to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}出租车！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我非常欣赏你的报告 教授 非常有感染力\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I enjoyed your testimony, professor. It was very spirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:34.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 谢谢 那正是我们来这里的目的 不是吗？要让大家看看\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, thank you. That's what we're here for, right? Put on a good show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:40.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}很对 我在想我能不能和你谈谈有关暖流迁移中断的理论呢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Quite. I was wondering if I could talk to you about your theory on abrupt climate shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我叫瑞博森 特里·瑞博森\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The name's Rapson. Terry Rapson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 瑞博森教授？海德兰中心的？- 就是我\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Professor Rapson? Of the Hedland Center? - That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我读过您有关洋流的论文\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've read your work on ocean currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:54.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们找个地方喝杯茶怎么样？- 非常好 如果能打到车的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- What do you say to a spot of tea? - Absolutely. If we can hail a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}欢迎您回来收看 这里是苏格兰格拉斯哥曼彻斯特联队\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Welcome back to Glasgow, Scotland, where Manchester United...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:23.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在客场以三比一领先凯尔特人队\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...Leads 3 - 1 over hometown Celtic.
