Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.83,0:32:09.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那么北大西洋暖流呢？那有什么关系？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What about the North Atlantic Current? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.04,0:32:14.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我昨晚接到了海德兰中心瑞博森教授的电话\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I got a call last night from Professor Rapson at the Hedland Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.41,0:32:16.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他认为暖流已经变化了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He thinks the current has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.15,0:32:20.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好啦 杰克 那怎么可能？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, come on, Jack. How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.65,0:32:23.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}暖流的形成取决于淡水与盐份间的微妙平衡\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The current depends upon a balance of salt and freshwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.82,0:32:26.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 这个我们都清楚 - 是的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- We all know that. - Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.56,0:32:30.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是从来没有人调查过极地冰雪的融化后\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...but no one knows how much freshwater has been dumped into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.56,0:32:33.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有多少淡水流入了大海\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...because of melting polar ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.40,0:32:37.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我想我们达到了一个盐分稀释的关键点了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I think we've hit a critical desalinization point.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.27,0:32:41.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这可以解释是什么造成了这种极端的天气\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It would explain what's driving this extreme weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.11,0:32:44.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}海德兰中心有一些令人信服的数据\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hedland had some pretty convincing data.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.07,0:32:49.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们已要求我将之输入我的古气候模型当中以预测今后的情况\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They've asked me to feed it into my paleoclimate model to track the next events.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.40,0:32:52.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你是说这些不正常的天气还会继续吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Are you suggesting these weather anomalies are gonna continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.22,0:32:55.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不仅仅是继续 会更糟\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Not just continue. Get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.99,0:33:03.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我认为我们遇到了一次巨大的气候转变\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I think we're on the verge of a major climate shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.97,0:33:11.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}汤姆 你准备和管理层怎么讲？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you gonna tell the Administration?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.43,0:33:15.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你想我应该讲什么？政府现在必须作好长期性准备了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What do you expect me to tell them? The government has to make preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.57,0:33:18.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 杰克 你有的只是一个理论 - 给我巨型机 我可以证明它\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- You have a theory. - Give me the mainframe. I'll prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.71,0:33:20.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不行\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.48,0:33:25.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你有四十八小时\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You have 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.45,0:33:27.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 霍尔教授 - 是\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Professor Hall. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.12,0:33:31.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我认为你的理论有可能是正确的 - 跟我来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- I think your theory may be correct. - Walk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.19,0:33:34.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}就在几个星期前 我观察到了最强烈的飓风记录\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just a few weeks ago, I monitored the strongest hurricane on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.82,0:33:37.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}冰雹 龙卷风 这些都合乎理论\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The hail, the tornados, it all fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.69,0:33:40.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你的模型能够模拟风暴下的形势吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Can your model factor in storm scenarios?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.50,0:33:43.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们没有时间 - 喔 也许我可以帮忙\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- We haven't had the time. - Well, maybe I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.90,0:33:45.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 欢迎加入 - 谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Welcome aboard. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.74,0:33:47.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嗨 我是詹森\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hi, I'm Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:50.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 嗨 - 嗨\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.21,0:33:54.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你有彼得的ＣＴ扫描结果吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Do you have Peter's CT scan results?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.24,0:33:56.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有 治疗让肿瘤减小了百分之二十\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah. The treatments shrunk the tumor 20 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.01,0:33:59.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 他今天的视力好点了吗？- 不 没有变化\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Is his eyesight better today? - No. No change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.89,0:34:13.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 嗨 彼得 你今天怎么样？- 好点了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Hi, Peter. How are you doing today? - A little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.76,0:34:15.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.07,0:34:18.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}让我来听听\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Let me listen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:20.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你能看见那上面的字了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Can you read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.00,0:34:25.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不能 但是我记得图片里讲的故事\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, but I remember the story from the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:26.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}是吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.24,0:34:29.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我妈妈以前经常读给我听\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}My mother used to read it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.75,0:34:33.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她一定会为你骄傲的 你这个勇敢的大男孩\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She must be very proud of you. You've been such a brave, big boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.55,0:34:37.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 谢谢 - 不客气\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.15,0:34:41.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 给你 - 谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Here you go. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:48.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克 你已经连续工作了二十四个小时\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack, you've been working for 24 hours straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.10,0:34:51.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你是唯一一个没有休息过的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're the only one who hasn't taken a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.14,0:34:55.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许我该眯一小会儿了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Maybe I'll try to shut my eyes for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.01,0:34:58.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果你拿到结果通知我\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Call me when you get the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}弗兰克 他总是这么专心吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Frank, is he always so obsessive?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.68,0:35:06.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 对 - 是的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Yeah. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.79,0:35:10.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他从来没放松过吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Does he ever lighten up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.35,0:35:12.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 没见过 - 没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Not really. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.53,0:35:19.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你们一起工作多长时间了？- 喔 弗兰克已经和他\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- How long have you been working together? - Well, Frank's been working with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.13,0:35:25.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}从石器时代就开始了 而我刚做了两年的苦役\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...since the Stone Age, but I've only had to endure two years of servitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.21,0:35:34.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.91,0:35:36.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克 我们拿到结果了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack, we got the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.36,0:35:47.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}六到八个月？那不可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Six to eight months? That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.66,0:35:51.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那时间不是按月算的 是按星期\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That time scale isn't in months. It's in weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:36:00.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}洪水已经造成多处设施关闭 包括林肯和荷兰隧道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Flooding has caused numerous closures, including the Lincoln and Holland Tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.20,0:36:05.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这所学校里的管道十分破旧 这种大雨 下水道很快就堵了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The plumbing in the school is really old. With this rain, the sewage got stopped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:07.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在哪里过夜？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.74,0:36:10.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们在为我们找住处\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They're finding a place for us with kids here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:12.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你肯定不能在明天之前回到家里吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You can't get home any sooner than tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.32,0:36:17.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 爸爸 如果我能的话 我会的 你知道 只是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, look, Dad, I would if I could, you know. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.76,0:36:21.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}气味太难闻了 爸爸\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This smell is unbearable, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.29,0:36:23.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}别再讲笑话了！ 我想让你尽早回家\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Stop kidding around! I want you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.43,0:36:25.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}爸爸 我会上火车的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Dad, I'll be on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.29,0:36:28.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}帮我个忙 就别担心我了 我会处理好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Do me a favor. Just don't worry about me. I'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.37,0:36:32.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧 儿子 我们明天见\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All right, son. I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.41,0:36:37.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 萨姆 猜怎么着？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, Sam, guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.94,0:36:40.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们找到个地方了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We got a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:42.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}太好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.61,0:36:47.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}到现在为止 恶劣气候还没有袭击华盛顿 本地居民不准备冒险\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}So far, the terrible weather hasn't hit D.C., but local residents aren't taking chances...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.15,0:36:51.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}人们纷纷抢购以防备被认为是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...as people stock up for what is already being billed as...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.92,0:36:54.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 有史以来最糟糕的风暴季节 - 你最好能确定\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}-...the worst storm season on record. - Better be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.59,0:36:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我可是生死寄于一线 - 你看过模型了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- My ass is on the line. - You saw the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.89,0:36:59.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我希望那是错的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And I hope to God it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:01.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 副总统先生 - 汤姆\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Mr. Vice President. - Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.56,0:37:04.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你认识霍尔教授 - 对 我们见过面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- You know Professor Hall. - Yes, we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.40,0:37:07.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}霍尔教授有些重要信息 我想你该看一看\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Professor Hall has some information I think you should look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:10.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们刚从模拟模型中得到了些结果\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We just got these results from our simulation model.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.81,0:37:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 他们会解释是什么导致了这样的天气 - 我等会儿会看的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- They explain what's causing this weather. - I'll read it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.10,0:37:17.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我必须先和联邦应急管理局开个会 - 这非常紧急\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- I have to meet with the director of FEMA...- This is very urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.61,0:37:21.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们的气候在六到八个星期之内将发生剧烈变化\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Our climate is changing violently. It will happen over the next six to eight weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:24.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你说过这在一百年内不会发生\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You said this wouldn't happen for another 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.92,0:37:27.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我错了 - 喔 那可能这次你也错了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- I was wrong. - Well, suppose you're wrong this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.76,0:37:30.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我希望我是错的 但是你必须意识到到处都发生了什么\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I wish I were, but you're aware of what's happening everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.09,0:37:35.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们已经为这次风暴做好了必要的准备 你还想我们做什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're making all the necessary preparations for this storm. What more do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.63,0:37:39.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你必须现在开始考虑进行大范围的疏散工作\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You have to start thinking about large-scale evacuations right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.67,0:37:41.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}特别是北部的州\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Especially in the Northern states.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.57,0:37:43.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 疏散？- 对\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Evacuations? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.31,0:37:46.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你疯了吗 霍尔？- 我必须走了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Have you lost your mind, Hall? - I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.84,0:37:52.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}副总统先生！ 如果我们现在不行动的话 那就太晚了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mr. Vice President! If we don't act now, it's going to be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.05,0:37:57.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来吧 杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.35,0:37:59.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}谢谢你带我们来这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thanks for bringing us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.16,0:38:04.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不能让你们还没有参观自然历史博物馆就走啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I couldn't let you leave New York without seeing the Natural History Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.19,0:38:07.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}当然不能 这是一个动物展览 一个个肚子满满的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Of course not. It's a fine collection of stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.23,0:38:08.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 哥们 来瞧瞧这个\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, guys, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.97,0:38:13.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这个猛犸象的尸体在西伯利亚冻土带被发现它保存完好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}"The body of this mammoth was found perfectly preserved in the Siberian tundra...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.40,0:38:18.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}它的嘴和胃里还有食物\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...with food still in its mouth and stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}说明它在吃草的时候被突然冻僵\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...indicating that it froze instantly while grazing."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.75,0:38:32.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}大雪降临英伦三岛已经二十四个小时了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's been 24 hours now since the snow started falling across the British Isles...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.09,0:38:36.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}北欧地区也是一样 而且丝毫没有停止的迹象\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and over Northern Europe. It shows no signs of letting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.33,0:38:39.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 你不要再担心了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, You've got to stop worrying. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.30,0:38:43.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}没问题 我们有充足的补给 我们只是被雪困住了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's fine. We've got plenty of supplies. We're just snowed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.47,0:38:45.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对 不 没关系 没关系\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah. No, it's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.04,0:38:48.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 不 你待在那里 - 我会没事的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- No, you stay where you are. - I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.37,0:38:51.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对 我也爱你 好 再见\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, I love you too. Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.48,0:38:56.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 嘿 珍妮特怎么样？- 喔 还好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Hey. How's Jeanette? - Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:38:58.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}渡船刚刚靠岸\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The ferry just landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.71,0:39:00.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}西班牙一定不错 真希望我能在那里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Must be nice in Spain. Wish I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.88,0:39:04.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}一支皇家空军的精锐直升机救助队已经被派出\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}An elite RAF search-and-rescue team has been deployed by helicopter...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.59,0:39:07.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}前往救助皇室成员到安全的地方\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...to airlift the royal family to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.59,0:39:11.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 哼 你想他们会来救我们吗？- 不太可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Yeah, you think they'll come get us? - Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.03,0:39:16.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}幸运的是我们自己有储备足够把船压沉的茶和甜品\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Luckily we've got our own genny, enough tea and biscuits to sink a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.63,0:39:18.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 我们会没事的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.73,0:39:21.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}只要厕所没问题就好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}As long as the loo doesn't back up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.42,0:39:44.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们的能见度为零 保持航向和速度\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got zero visibility. Maintain heading and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.76,0:39:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们的航向？- 035 长官\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What's our heading? 035, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.23,0:39:50.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}大约离巴尔莫罗城堡还有四十公里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Approximately 40 kilometers from Balmoral Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.33,0:39:52.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们看不到你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've lost visual contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.79,0:40:19.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 这块表出毛病了 - 风速降为零\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- This gauge can't be right. - Wind speed has dropped to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.00,0:40:22.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们遇到了垂直的环状云团\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We have vertical walls of cirrus cloud formations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.37,0:40:28.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 到底发生了什么事？- 该死的油管被冻死了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- What the hell is going on? - The bloody fuel lines are starting to freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.11,0:40:41.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}引擎压力正在下降 螺旋桨转速在下降\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Port engine pressure is dropping. The rotor rpm is dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.02,0:40:45.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们的右弦熄火\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got a flameout on the starboard side as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.66,0:40:50.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}做好撞地准备\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Prepare for crash landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.30,0:40:54.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}使用紧急燃油\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Select emergency fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.33,0:40:57.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来呀 该死的！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.03,0:40:59.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}起来！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.19,0:41:25.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我要对你说的是保密的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What I'm about to say is supposed to be confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.16,0:41:29.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}几小时前 三架直升机在苏格兰坠毁\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Several hours ago, three helicopters went down over Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.07,0:41:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}它们因为燃油在管道内冻结而坠毁\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They crashed because the fuel in their lines froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.37,0:41:38.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 在什么温度下？- 华氏零下150度 [摄氏零下101度]\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- At what temperature does? - Negative 150 degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.74,0:41:40.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们必须查一下\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We had to look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:42.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}气温下降的速度非常快\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The temperature dropped phenomenally fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.91,0:41:46.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在地面上 人们在没爬出汽车之前就被冻僵了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}On the ground, people froze before they could get out of their cars even.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.78,0:41:49.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你能给我一份两小时前苏格兰地区的卫星图吗？- 好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Can you get a satellite picture of Scotland two hours ago? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.89,0:41:52.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们数据堆积成山\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got mountains of data...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.22,0:41:56.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是却没有足够的计算机资源来分析它 你能帮帮我们吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...but nowhere near enough computer power to analyze it. Can you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.39,0:41:58.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}把你得到的数据传给我们 我们尽力而为\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Send us what you got. We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.56,0:42:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}谢谢 杰克 再见\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thanks, Jack. Bye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.53,0:42:06.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这是气温下降时候的苏格兰\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This is Scotland at the time the temperature dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.47,0:42:10.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这情况看起来就象飓风一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This thing looks just like a hurricane.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.94,0:42:13.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}只是飓风不能在地面形成\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Only hurricanes don't form over land.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.38,0:42:23.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 晚上好 先生 - 嘿 哈罗德\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Good evening, sir. - Hey, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.99,0:42:26.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 谢谢 维克托 明早见 - 好的 先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Thanks, Victor. See you in the morning. - Right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.89,0:42:28.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 糟糕的天气 - 给我说说看\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Terrible weather. - Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.40,0:42:34.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}哇\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.70,0:42:38.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你就住这？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.37,0:42:40.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}只是在周末的时候\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.37,0:42:43.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这是我爸爸的地方 他不经常在家 于是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's my dad's place. He's kind of never around, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:44.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他在哪？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.77,0:42:47.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}和我继母在欧洲滑雪\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Skiing in Europe with my stepmom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.75,0:42:52.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这是你和你兄弟吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Is this you and your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.65,0:42:55.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对 那时我们一起骑车\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, that's when we took a bike trip together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.02,0:43:03.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这样的雨到现在为止已经下了三天了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's been raining like this for three days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.84,0:43:16.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 快点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.15,0:43:31.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我只是站在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm just standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.25,0:43:33.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你不能待在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.96,0:43:35.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}反正我从来不喜欢这里的社区\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I never liked this neighborhood anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.13,0:43:38.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在大中心车站是一片慌乱的景象\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's a mob scene here at Grand Central Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.86,0:43:44.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有一半以上的站台已经被淹没 所有的火车服务已经终止\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Over half the platforms are flooded and service has been suspended on all trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.23,0:43:47.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}飞机仍然停在机场而火车现在也停止服务\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}With planes still grounded and trains now out of service...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.50,0:43:49.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这真是个坏消息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...that's bad news for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.41,0:43:53.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}维克托来接我了 你们需要搭车去火车站吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Victor's coming to pick me up. You guys want a ride to the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.68,0:43:54.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不用了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.11,0:44:00.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在诺瓦斯科舌 今早在数秒中之内海浪就升高了25英尺\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}In Nova Scotia earlier today the ocean rose by 25 feet in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.68,0:44:04.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们在几天前所担心的终于发生了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What we have feared for the past few days has indeed happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.49,0:44:06.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}冷空气前锋已经从北极移动\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The cold front moving from the Arctic...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.76,0:44:09.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在加拿大形成了巨大的风暴系统\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...has created an enormous storm system in Canada...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.59,0:44:13.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}听起来很难相信 但它看起来更象一个热带的飓风\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...which, incredible as it sounds, looks more like a tropical hurricane...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.60,0:44:16.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我要去接我的弟弟 你们要搭车吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I gotta go pick up my little brother. Do you guys want a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.10,0:44:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 他在哪？- 他在费城的寄宿学校\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Where is he? - He's in a boarding school in Philadelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.50,0:44:21.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果这个系统移向南方\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}If this system moves south...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.17,0:44:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们就将看见海啸在风力驱使下侵袭整个东海岸\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...we could see a wind-driven storm surge threaten the entire Eastern Seaboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.71,0:44:29.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧 再见\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.15,0:44:32.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}维克托的车被堵在了第五街口\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Victor's stuck in traffic over on Fifth Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.85,0:44:36.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果我们能在那里和他碰头的话出城会更方便一点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It'll be easier to head out of town if we meet him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.19,0:44:39.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你是说走去？不 不能象这样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You mean walk? No, not in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.89,0:44:44.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们应该走楼梯\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We should take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.83,0:44:47.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们可在顶层\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're on the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.43,0:44:52.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我猜我们得走着下去了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I guess we're walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.21,0:45:07.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许我们应该等在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Maybe we should just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.28,0:45:08.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我认为这位小姐说得对\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I think the young lady is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.29,0:45:11.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 我们必须回家\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No. We need to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.41,0:45:38.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 西斯 这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, Cesar, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.98,0:45:40.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在干什么呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.72,0:45:48.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}狼 它们跑了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The wolves, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.59,0:45:50.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这只是让你们能大概了解一下\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just to give you an idea of the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.96,0:45:54.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这里的情况每况愈下\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...which seems to be becoming worse with each passing minute:
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.26,0:45:57.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}现在 在岛上的大部分地区都出现了洪水\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}At the moment, we have flooding in most parts of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.00,0:46:01.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在曼哈顿大部分市区内 因为电力中断\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got traffic snarl-ups because the electricity is now out...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.54,0:46:05.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}交通已经瘫痪了 没有交通灯\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...to almost every part of Manhattan. No traffic signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.24,0:46:07.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}最少有两百起汽车事故\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Car accidents, at least two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.74,0:46:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}而下曼哈顿区 我们已被告知 几乎无法进入\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And lower Manhattan, we've been told, is virtually inaccessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.37,0:46:35.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你能打电话给妈妈吗？你能打电话找她吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Can you call Mom? Will you please phone her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.07,0:46:37.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.51,0:46:39.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}狗不允许进入\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That dog can't come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.11,0:46:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我说 哥们 外面瓢泼大雨啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, man. It's pouring out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.78,0:46:44.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不管 看那个标示\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I don't care. Read the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.97,0:46:46.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}{\fs12\bord0\shad1\b1}{\fsp1}{\pos(190,50)}{\frz-0.8}{\fscx90\fscy130}请勿携带食品 饮料及宠物入内
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.92,0:46:49.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这可是个公共图书馆\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's supposed to be a public library.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.99,0:46:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 哥们 这边\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, guys, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.59,0:47:00.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起 你的包\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Excuse me. Your bad.
