Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.30,0:59:54.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.04,1:00:03.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我的手在发抖\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}My hands are shak...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.25,1:00:06.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 发抖 - 没关系 这样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Shaking. That's okay. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.85,1:00:08.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这样 这样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.56,1:00:14.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在干什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.56,1:00:17.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我用体温来给你取暖\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm using my body heat to warm you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.29,1:00:22.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果你四肢回血太快的话 你的心脏会承受不了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}If we let the blood from your arms and legs rush back to your heart too quickly...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.60,1:00:25.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你的心脏会停止跳动\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...your heart could fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.14,1:00:32.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在哪学的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.78,1:00:38.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}总有些人在生理卫生课上用心听了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Some of us were actually paying attention in health class.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.05,1:00:43.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你觉的怎么样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.42,1:00:47.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好多了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Much better.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.20,1:00:56.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}弗兰克告诉我有关萨姆的事了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Frank told me about Sam.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.77,1:01:00.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不是来劝你不要去的 但是我要你先办点别的事情\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm not gonna try to talk you out of going, but there's something I need first.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.10,1:01:03.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你必须把你的结果报告给管理层\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You have to explain your results to the Administration.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.04,1:01:06.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我已经试过了 汤姆 - 我知道 这次不一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- I already tried that, Tom. - I know. It'll be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.61,1:01:09.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你将直接给总统做简报\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're gonna brief the president directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.41,1:01:14.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 就这些了吗？- 差不多\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Is that the last of it? - Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.68,1:01:16.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.45,1:01:19.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们还发现了这个收音机 但是我想不好使了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We also found this radio, but I don't think it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.89,1:01:21.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}让我来看一看\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.10,1:01:29.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}狗狗 安静点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Buddha, keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.07,1:01:32.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你本来就不该来这\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You aingt even supposed to be in here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.36,1:02:29.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 伙计们\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.90,1:02:38.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 我的天啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.42,1:03:03.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}风暴的基本规则是它们会一直继续\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The basic rule of storms is they continue...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.79,1:03:07.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}直到产生它们的条件被破坏为止\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...until the imbalance that created them is corrected.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.30,1:03:10.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}现在 我们说的是全球重新调整\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}In this case, we're talking about a global realignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.20,1:03:14.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这次超级风暴会持续七到十天\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This superstorm will last 7 to 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.30,1:03:19.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}当它结束时 冰雪会覆盖整个北半球\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}When it's over, ice and snow will cover the entire Northern Hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.58,1:03:22.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}冰雪会反射阳光\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The ice and snow will reflect sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.31,1:03:24.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}而地球气候会重新平衡\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The Earth's atmosphere will restabilize...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.61,1:03:27.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}保持和上一个冰川时代相同的气温\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...with an average temperature close to that of the last Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.25,1:03:32.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 我们能做什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, what can we do about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.72,1:03:35.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}向南走 越远越好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Head as far south as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.39,1:03:37.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这并不好笑 教授\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That is not amusing, professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.36,1:03:40.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你建议他们去哪？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where do you suggest they go?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.60,1:03:43.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们向南走的越远他们就越安全\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The farther south they go, the safer they'll be.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.20,1:03:47.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}德克萨斯 佛罗里达州部分没有被淹的地方 墨西哥最好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Texas. Parts of Florida that aren't flooded. Mexico would be best.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.04,1:03:51.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}墨西哥？也许你该去管你的科学 让我们来决定政策\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mexico? Maybe you should stick to science and leave policy to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.81,1:03:53.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 这办法我们已经试过了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, we tried that approach.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.51,1:03:57.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在这还管用的时候 你听不进科学的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You didn't want to hear about the science when it could have made a difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.38,1:04:01.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你到底有什么建议 教授？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What exactly are you proposing, professor?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.99,1:04:13.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}疏散所有这条线以南的人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Evacuate everyone south of that line.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.79,1:04:20.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那线以北的人怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What about the people in the North?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.13,1:04:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}很遗憾 现在对他们来说已经太晚了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm afraid it's too late for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.67,1:04:27.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果他们走出去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}If they go outside...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.00,1:04:29.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}风暴会杀死他们\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...the storm will kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.24,1:04:35.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}到了这个时候\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}At this point...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.11,1:04:38.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们最大的生存机会是留在屋里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...their best chance is to stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.98,1:04:42.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}尽可能安全渡过\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Try to ride it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.88,1:04:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}祈祷\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.42,1:04:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你想他们会怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What do you think he'll do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.13,1:04:52.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.16,1:04:54.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.36,1:04:56.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.93,1:04:58.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}祝你好运\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.47,1:05:00.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你也一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.27,1:05:04.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们都需要好运气\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're all gonna need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.34,1:05:12.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们不能因为一个科学家认为气候在转变就疏散半个国家\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We can't evacuate half the country because one scientist thinks the climate is shifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.58,1:05:16.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 耽误每一分钟都要付出生命代价 - 那另一半国家怎么办？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Every minute we delay costs lives. - What about the other half of the country?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.68,1:05:18.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果霍尔教授对风暴的预测是正确的话\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}If Professor Hall is right about this storm...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.15,1:05:21.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}派军队到北方只会造成更大的伤亡\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...sending troops north will create more victims.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.76,1:05:24.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们必须现在就开始救我们能救的人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We need to save the people we can right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.33,1:05:27.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们在战场上也会选择性救治 这种情况很像\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We take the same approach in triage on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.56,1:05:30.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有时作出艰难的选择是有必要的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sometimes it's necessary to make difficult choices...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.77,1:05:33.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不认为抛弃半个国家是必要的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I don't accept abandoning half the country as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.84,1:05:36.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果你早点听他的话 也许确实没必要\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Maybe if you listened sooner, it wouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.34,1:05:38.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}胡说 对他来说很建议一下很容易\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Bullshit. It's easy for him to suggest this plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.94,1:05:42.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他在华盛顿很安全 他的儿子在曼哈顿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He's safely here in Washington. His son is in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.78,1:05:49.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我认为在你置疑他的动机之前你应该了解这一点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I thought you should know before you start questioning his motives.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.69,1:05:53.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们准备执行霍尔的计划\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're going to follow Hall's plan.
