Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.81,1:06:20.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}给我接我的妻子\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...get me my wife.
