Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.34,1:06:47.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.31,1:06:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有没有可能\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Is there any chance...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.51,1:06:51.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们可以...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...that it'll run...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.25,1:06:55.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}用这个？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...on this?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.32,1:06:56.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你疯了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.08,1:06:59.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那是放了十二年的苏格兰威士忌\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That's a 12-year-old Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.24,1:07:22.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}先生们\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.44,1:07:25.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}为了英国\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}To England.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.48,1:07:28.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}为了人类\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}To mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.42,1:07:32.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}为了曼彻斯特联队\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}To Manchester United.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.13,1:07:41.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我只是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.60,1:07:45.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我只是希望我能看着他长大 你知道吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I just wish I could have seen him grow up. You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.20,1:07:52.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}最重要的是他会长大的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The important thing is he will grow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.04,1:07:58.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}阿门\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.40,1:08:18.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许你应该找别人帮帮你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Maybe you should have somebody help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.80,1:08:21.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}先生 我是电子学生会的主席\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sir, I am president of the Electronics Club...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.77,1:08:24.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}还有数学和象棋协会\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...the Math Club and the Chess Club.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.21,1:08:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}现在 如果这里有个更牛的人 请把他指出来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Now, if there's a bigger nerd in here, please, point him out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.64,1:08:32.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我最好让你自己继续干 好吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'll just leave you alone to work on it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.85,1:08:36.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 狗狗 来 解决你的个人问题吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, Buddha, come on. Do your business.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.05,1:08:39.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}看 这里没别人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Look, there's nobody around.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.02,1:08:42.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你知道吗？我转过去 我不会看的 我保证\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You know what? I'll turn around. I won't look. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.09,1:08:48.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.47,1:08:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 哥们 有很多人在外面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, man, there's people out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.74,1:08:59.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我在溜狗\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I was walking my dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.21,1:09:03.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}有好几百人 他们在雪上走\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}There's hundreds of them. They're walking on the snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.22,1:09:12.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们去哪？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where they all going?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.92,1:09:15.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们要离开城市 要不然就太晚了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They're getting out of the city before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.96,1:09:21.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧 所有人 安静\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All right, everybody. Quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.10,1:09:25.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}最后一个人收到手机信号是在什么时候？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}When was the last time anyone got a signal on a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.23,1:09:27.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我在一个小时前刚接通我在孟菲斯的表亲\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I got through to my cousin in Memphis an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.00,1:09:29.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们已经开始向南方疏散了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They're being evacuated to the South.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.04,1:09:31.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们也应该走\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We should get moving too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.74,1:09:34.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}水已经被冻得足够结实 可以走了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The water is frozen over enough to walk on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.54,1:09:37.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们应该在雪太深之前赶紧离开\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We should get going before the snow gets too deep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.95,1:09:41.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}所有人 以最快速度裹好自己\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Everyone, wrap yourselves up as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.75,1:09:43.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们不应该走\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We shouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.35,1:09:45.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}为什么不 萨姆？大家都在离开\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Why not, Sam? Everyone's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.39,1:09:48.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}当我和我爸爸通电话的时候 他告诉我要待在屋子里面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}When I talked to my dad, he told me to stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.26,1:09:49.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他说风暴会杀死所有在风暴里的人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The storm will kill anybody in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.16,1:09:52.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 那你该让大家知道 - 我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Then you have to say something. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.03,1:09:59.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起 先生 你正在犯一个错误\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Excuse me, sir, you're making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.73,1:10:02.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}什么？听着 我们都很害怕 但是我们别无选择\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What? Listen, we're all scared, but we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.84,1:10:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我不是说这个 - 准备好离开吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- That's not it. - Get ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.61,1:10:08.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}如果这些人走出去 他们会被冻死！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}If these people go outside, they will freeze to death!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.94,1:10:10.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好 这些都是什么无稽之谈？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, what is this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.88,1:10:14.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这不是无稽之谈 好吗？看 风暴将越来越强\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's not nonsense. All right? Look, this storm is gonna get worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.72,1:10:17.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}人在外面会被冻死\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The people caught outside will freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.32,1:10:20.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你从哪里知道的？- 我爸爸是气象学家\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Where are you getting this? - My dad's a climatologist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.25,1:10:22.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 他为政府工作 - 我们该怎么做\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- He works for the government. - So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.06,1:10:25.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们应该留在室内取暖 然后等待风暴过去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We stay inside, we keep warm, and we wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.89,1:10:28.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}雪每一分钟都在越积越厚\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The snow is getting deeper by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.20,1:10:30.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们困在这里 没有食品 没有补给\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We'd be trapped here without food, supplies...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.93,1:10:33.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 是很冒险 对...- 是不必要的冒险\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's a risk, yeah...- An unnecessary risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.20,1:10:34.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 不 不是\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, no. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.64,1:10:37.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们已经浪费够多的时间讨论这个了 来吧 大伙\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've wasted enough time talking. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.20,1:10:38.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}咱们走吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.71,1:10:42.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 听着 听着 就听一秒钟 - 来 所有人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Look, look. Just look for a second. - Come on, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.24,1:10:45.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}风暴正在加强 它会越来越猛烈\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This storm is gonna get bad. It's gonna get really, really bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.85,1:10:47.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你们无法活下来的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're not gonna be able to survive it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.25,1:10:50.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}相信我\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.72,1:10:55.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}先生们 请留下来 留下来吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sir, please just stay. Just stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.86,1:10:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不要...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.12,1:11:30.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她可以走了 来 直接到后面 伙计们\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She's set to go. Come on, straight to the back, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.42,1:11:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们没法保持联系的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It'll be impossible to reach each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:35.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}（你到了）在墨西哥城的领事馆留条消息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Leave a message for me at the embassy in Mexico City.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.50,1:11:36.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好 我会的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.37,1:11:39.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我爱你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.24,1:11:45.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我爱你 杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I love you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.47,1:11:49.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}告诉萨姆我非常爱他\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Tell Sam I love him so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.88,1:11:52.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}愿主保佑你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.99,1:12:02.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 霍尔医生？- 在\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Doctor Hall? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.19,1:12:04.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们无法联系到彼得的父母\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We haven't been able to reach Peter's parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.73,1:12:08.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我会迟些再试 好吗？- 好 谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- I'm gonna try later, okay? - Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.70,1:12:17.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我自己就能搬动\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.51,1:12:21.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你应该在向南方开的客车上\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're supposed to be on a bus heading south.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.31,1:12:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我已经照看你二十年了 你以为我会让你一个人去吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've been watching your back for 20 years. You think I'd let you go alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.98,1:12:29.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这么多年我还以为一直是我在照看你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And all these years I thought I was watching your back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.38,1:12:31.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}钥匙在哪里？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where are the keys?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.32,1:12:33.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在卡车里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}In the truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.65,1:12:36.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你又想去哪？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.22,1:12:38.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你们中任何一个都不懂得导航\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Neither one of you can navigate worth a damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.83,1:12:40.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}没有我 你们会跑到克里夫兰的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Without me, you'll end up in Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.03,1:12:46.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}一路上我会尽力给你提供风暴的最新信息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'll try to give you updates on the storm as it heads your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.80,1:12:48.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}祝你好运 杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Good luck, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.48,1:13:05.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来自美墨边界的惊人消息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Breaking news from the U.S. - Mexico border.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.35,1:13:08.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}就在半小时之前 墨西哥当局关闭了边界\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just half an hour ago, Mexican officials closed the border...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.89,1:13:12.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}因为太多美国难民逃往南方\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...in the light of so many U.S. Refugees who are fleeing south...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.73,1:13:14.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}而这都是因为逼近的风暴\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...in the wake of the approaching storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.13,1:13:18.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这些人来到这里 希望能进入墨西哥\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}These people came in anticipation of crossing into Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.30,1:13:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}然而 他们被拒之门外\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Instead, they've been met with closed gates.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.67,1:13:23.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}现在 在一个戏剧性的反向非法移民浪潮中\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And now, in a dramatic reversal of illegal immigration...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.14,1:13:27.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}成千上万的人穿过格兰德河逃往墨西哥\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...thousands of people are crossing the Rio Grande into Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.88,1:13:31.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在我身后展现的是一幅绝望和失望的场面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The scene unfolding here behind me is one of desperation and frustration.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.75,1:13:35.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}人们丢弃他们的汽车带上他们的东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}People have abandoned their cars, grabbed their belongings...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.42,1:13:40.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}非法渡河到墨西哥\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and they are wading across the river illegally into Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.42,1:13:44.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}就是这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.53,1:13:48.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}火炉差不多有一百年没有用了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This fireplace probably hasn't been used in about 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.63,1:13:53.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.84,1:14:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你在干什么？- 你以为我们要烧什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- What are you doing? - What did you think we would burn?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.98,1:14:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你不能烧书 - 不 绝对不能\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- You can't burn books. - No, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.28,1:14:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你想冻死吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You want to freeze to death?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.15,1:14:13.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我去找更多的来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'll go get some more.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.39,1:14:14.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我来帮你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.32,1:14:17.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我跟他们一起去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm going with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.73,1:14:21.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好 这里有咖啡屋或者午餐室吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, do you have a cafeteria or a lunchroom?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.36,1:14:24.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}只有一个职员的休息室和几个自动售货机\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just an employees'lounge with a few vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.11,1:14:34.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们只靠Ｍ＆Ｍ豆和薯片不可能支持很久的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're not gonna last long on M&M's and potato chips.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.88,1:14:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}垃圾桶呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What about the garbage cans?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.18,1:14:39.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在垃圾桶里总有吃的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}There's always something to eat in the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.85,1:14:46.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 尼采的书？- 我们不能烧尼采的书\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Friedrich Nietzsche? - We can't burn Nietzsche.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.69,1:14:49.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他是十九世纪最重要的思想家\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He was the most important thinker of the 19th century.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.86,1:14:52.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}别扯了 他是个狂妄的沙文主义者 还爱上了他妹妹\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Please. He was a chauvinist pig in love with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.06,1:14:54.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他不是狂妄的扩张主义者\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He was not a chauvinist pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.13,1:14:57.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是他爱上了他妹妹对吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}But he was in love with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.30,1:14:58.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起？ 伙计们？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Excuse me? You guys?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.13,1:15:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对了 这里有一区的关于税法的书我们可以拿来烧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, there's a whole section on tax law down here that we can burn.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.47,1:15:06.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在数小时的不稳定以后 交通现在又恢复了正常\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}After hours of uncertainty, the traffic is now moving smoothly...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.04,1:15:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}从美国到墨西哥\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...from the United States into Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.41,1:15:13.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这是因为总统同墨西哥政府达成了一个协议\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This is only possible because the president was able to negotiate a deal...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.45,1:15:17.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}以免除所有拉丁美洲国家的债务为代价 开放所有边界\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...to forgive all Latin American debt in exchange for opening the border.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.02,1:15:22.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}现在 美国的众多家庭终于大松了口气\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Now, multitudes of American families are feeling a rush of relief...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.86,1:15:27.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}露西？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.47,1:15:34.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}彼得的救护车在这里了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Is Peter's ambulance here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.14,1:15:36.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}没有\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.01,1:15:44.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 为什么？- 他们都走了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Why? - They've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.65,1:15:46.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 什么？- 在混乱之中...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- What? - In the confusion...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.38,1:15:50.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我不知道到底发生了什么 人们开始惊慌 然后他们就离开了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...I don't know what happened. People started to panic, and they left...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.25,1:15:52.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 上帝啊 - 有个警察带着雪橇\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- God. - There's a policeman with a snowplow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.69,1:15:55.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 他在外面等着 - 天啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- He's waiting outside. - God.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.29,1:15:57.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}彼得除了救护车之外什么也不能坐\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Peter can't be moved in anything but an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.56,1:16:02.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我已经打过电话给郡救护车中心留了口信\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I called and left a message for the county ambulance service.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.50,1:16:12.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.34,1:16:16.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好的 你应该走了 我留下来等\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, you should go, and I'll stay and wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.28,1:16:18.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}露西 不\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Lucy, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.71,1:16:20.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 不 - 你应该走\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- No. - No, you should go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.71,1:16:22.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他不会等太久的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He's not gonna wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.82,1:16:24.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}没关系\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.25,1:16:29.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.02,1:16:32.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 没关系 - 好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's okay. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.29,1:17:02.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你还好吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.06,1:17:06.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我还好 我只是...我那天把腿割伤了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, I'm fine. I just...I cut my leg the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.20,1:17:11.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你接收到信号了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Did you get a signal?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.67,1:17:13.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}是的 就一会\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah, for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.93,1:17:15.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}还有别的吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.21,1:17:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}兄弟 这次到处都是风暴\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Man, this storm is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.58,1:17:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}它席卷了整个北半球\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's hit the entire Northern Hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.68,1:17:27.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}欧洲被埋在十五英尺厚的积雪底下\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Europe is buried under 15 feet of snow...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.41,1:17:30.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们说这里的情况也会一样\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and they say it's gonna get just as bad here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.72,1:17:33.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我是说 我想你爸爸到不了这里了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I mean, I don't think your dad's gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.32,1:17:38.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 他会来的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, he'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.66,1:17:45.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他会来的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.10,1:17:52.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}白宫已经对于所有北部的州\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The White House has ordered a national disaster alert...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.11,1:17:54.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}发布了全国灾难警报\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...for all Northern states.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.68,1:17:57.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}持续暴露在风暴中是有致命危险的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Continued exposure to the approaching storm is deadly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.58,1:18:01.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}留在室内 想尽一切办法取暖 使用所有可能的燃料\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Remain indoors and take all measures to stay warm, burning any fuel sources...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.75,1:18:05.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}直到风暴结束 从纽约州一直到宾夕法尼亚州\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...until the storm is over. Roads are impassable across New York State...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.62,1:18:07.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}所有街道都无法通行\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...as far south as Pennsylvania...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.09,1:18:09.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们在哪？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.06,1:18:14.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}看起来我们只走到了费城北部\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Looks like we're just north of Philadelphia.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.20,1:18:19.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}小心！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.17,1:18:25.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你们怎么样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.11,1:18:27.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}还好 还好\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.55,1:18:36.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 再说一次 所有经过的道路...- 对不起 老板\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Once again, roads across the...- Sorry, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.48,1:18:39.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}穿上雪靴\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Unpack the snowshoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.05,1:18:41.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们从这里开始步行\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're walking from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.56,1:18:46.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 女士 我们起来继续前进\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, ma'am. Let's get up and get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.56,1:18:51.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们只到了布鲁克林 也许我们应该走回去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've only made it to Brooklyn. Maybe we should just turn back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.43,1:18:55.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}为什么？半个城市已经被冻住了 没有回去的理由了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Why? Half the city's frozen under water. There's nothing to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.20,1:18:56.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}到了起床赶路的时候了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Time to get up and keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.94,1:18:59.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许我们应该待在图书馆里面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What we should've done is stayed in the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.38,1:19:04.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好了 伙计 咱们继续走吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, guys, let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.65,1:19:15.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}醒醒\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.21,1:19:34.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在干什么呢？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.84,1:19:36.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}隔绝热量散失\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Insulating.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.74,1:19:39.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}报纸是最好的 但是这个也可以\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Newspaper's best, but this'll do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.51,1:19:43.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你知道 你要是在大街上过上几年 你就会学会取暖\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You know, you spend some years on the streets and you learn how to keep warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.45,1:19:46.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.56,1:19:53.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}谢谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.06,1:19:59.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我想到一个\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I got one.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.20,1:20:01.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你最难忘的假期\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Your favorite vacation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.97,1:20:04.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这个不算？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Besides this one?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.91,1:20:07.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.37,1:20:11.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}几年前 我同我父亲一同去格陵兰进行一项他的研究\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I went to Greenland with my dad on one of his research trips a few years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.98,1:20:18.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}船出了故障 我们被困\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and the ship broke down, and we got stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.59,1:20:22.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}天总是在下雨\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And it rained constantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.02,1:20:26.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}听起来很没意思啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That sounds really boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.49,1:20:29.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是实际上很有意思 你知道吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}But actually really nice, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.16,1:20:33.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}只有我和我爸爸一起渡过了十天\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Just me and my dad hanging out for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.21,1:21:47.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}弗兰克！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Frank!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.28,1:21:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你怎么样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.08,1:21:51.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我没事\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.05,1:21:55.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我只是掉下去 可以买点东西了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I just dropped in to do a little shopping.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.08,1:21:58.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我得把雪橇扔了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I gotta lose this sled.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.90,1:22:17.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}坚持住！我们把你拉上来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hold on! We'll pull you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.17,1:22:23.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}詹森！你必须支撑住弗兰克的体重\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jason! You've got to support Frank's weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.34,1:22:26.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好的 我试一试\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.49,1:22:35.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好的 我想现在我支撑住他的体重了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay, I think I have his weight now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.29,1:22:37.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我正向你靠近\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.74,1:22:52.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}玻璃碎了！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The glass is breaking!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.51,1:22:55.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}太重了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Too much weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.88,1:23:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不可能支撑住的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's not gonna hold.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.22,1:23:12.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 不要\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.89,1:23:15.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}弗兰克 我可以把你拉上来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Frank. I can get you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.16,1:23:19.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}别那么做！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.83,1:23:22.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 不 弗兰克 不要！- 弗兰克 不要！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- No, Frank, no! - Frank, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.90,1:23:25.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}弗兰克！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Frank!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.28,1:24:11.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你拿的是什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.09,1:24:14.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}一本古腾堡印刷的圣经\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}A Gutenberg Bible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.69,1:24:16.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在稀有图书室里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It was in the rare books room.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.29,1:24:19.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你以为上帝会来解救你吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You think God's gonna save you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.76,1:24:23.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 我不信上帝\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No. I don't believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.20,1:24:26.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但你把圣经抓的很紧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You're holding onto that Bible pretty tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.03,1:24:29.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我在保护它\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.54,1:24:36.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这本圣经是第一本印刷的书\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This Bible is the first book ever printed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.88,1:24:41.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}它代表着一个思想时代的开始\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It represents the dawn of the age of reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.22,1:24:46.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对我来说 文字是人类最大的成就\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}As far as I'm concerned, the written word is mankind's greatest achievement.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.59,1:24:48.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你可以笑\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You can laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.12,1:24:52.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}但是如果西方文明终结了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}But if Western civilization is finished...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.89,1:24:56.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我最少可以保留其中一小片\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...I'm gonna save at least one little piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.63,1:25:35.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们听说有人掉队了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We heard somebody was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.70,1:25:40.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们带来了救护车 - 感谢上帝\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- We brought an ambulance. - Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.88,1:25:45.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}感谢你们能来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.53,1:26:08.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.97,1:26:11.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 你还好吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.41,1:26:14.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你看起来有点像发烧什么的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You look like you have a fever or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.77,1:26:17.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我没事 我只是睡不着\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm fine. I just can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.81,1:26:26.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我的脑子里全是那些没用的百科竞赛的事情\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}My mind keeps going over all those worthless decathlon facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.95,1:26:30.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 很傻 哈？- 不 没关系\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's pretty stupid, huh? - No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.42,1:26:33.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我猜你只是还没来得及调整\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I guess you just haven't had time to adjust yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.70,1:26:38.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我该怎么调整呢 萨姆？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How am I supposed to adjust, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.87,1:26:42.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我所关心的所有事情 我所努力的所有事情\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Everything I've ever cared about, everything I've worked for...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.34,1:26:46.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}都是为将来所准备的 可将来已经不存在了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...has all been preparation for a future that no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.44,1:26:54.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我知道你总觉得我把竞赛看得太重了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I know you always thought I took the competition too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.78,1:26:57.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你是对的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.22,1:27:01.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 那都是没用的 - 不 不 我...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It was all for nothing. - No, no. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.12,1:27:06.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 我只是...我那么说只是为了避免承认一个事实\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, I just...I just said that to avoid admitting the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.79,1:27:09.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}什么事实？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Truth about what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.50,1:27:16.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}关于我为什么加入比赛\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}About why I joined the team.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.01,1:27:24.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我参加是因为你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I joined it because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.26,1:27:38.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.52,1:28:06.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.59,1:28:07.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.99,1:28:10.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}总统先生 好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mr. President. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.79,1:28:13.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起 先生 我们不能再等了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm sorry, sir, we can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.76,1:28:15.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们是最后一队\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're the last ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.66,1:28:18.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.25,1:28:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}墨西卡利控制中心 这里是德尔塔26\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mexicali Control, this is Delta 26.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.60,1:28:37.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}{\fs14\bord0\shad3\b1}{\fsp1}{\pos(192,236)}{\fad(800,800)}墨西哥 美国难民营
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.62,1:28:38.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们接到统帅部紧急命令\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got an urgent message for high command.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.75,1:28:40.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}要求优先在一区降落\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Request priority for landing zone one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.12,1:28:45.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}收到 德尔塔26 运输机会等待的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Roger that, Delta 26. Transport will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.16,1:28:51.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 长官 - 谢谢 下士\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sir. Thank you, corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.70,1:28:53.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 对不起 来晚了 长官 - 继续\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sorry for the delay, sir. Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.68,1:29:08.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}秘书女士\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Madam Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.09,1:29:19.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}雷蒙德\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.66,1:29:23.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}总统的车队被困在风暴中\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The president's motorcade got caught in the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.23,1:29:29.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他们没能挺过来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}They didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.21,1:29:38.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她早晨就没醒来 我...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And she wouldn't wake up this morning. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.91,1:29:41.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我是说 昨晚她只是有点发烧 我不明白\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She only had a fever. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.51,1:29:43.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她脸色很苍白\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She's awfully pale.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.92,1:29:46.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们这几天都没有好好吃东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}None of us has had anything real to eat in days.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.55,1:29:49.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 这是低温症 - 但是怎么可能是低温症？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's hypothermia. - But how can it be hypothermia?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.72,1:29:51.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们都已经...- 也许是感冒\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- We've all been in...- Maybe it's the flu.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.96,1:29:54.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不 不 不是感冒\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}No, no, it's not the flu.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.50,1:29:56.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你怎么知道？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And how do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.20,1:30:00.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}书除了被焚烧外还有更有用处 她有什么症状？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Books can be good for things other than burning. What are her symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.97,1:30:04.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我告诉过你她在几天前发过烧 她还出冷汗\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I told you that she has a fever and her...She's got a really cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.87,1:30:06.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她的脉搏怎么样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How's her pulse?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.07,1:30:09.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 非常快 - 她受过什么外伤吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's really fast. - Does she have any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.64,1:30:12.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}也许是划伤引发感染？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Like a cut that might have gotten infected?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.35,1:30:15.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她几天前说过她的腿划伤了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She was complaining about a cut on her leg a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.38,1:30:19.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我没多想\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I didn't think anything of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.69,1:30:25.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}喔 我的天啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.63,1:30:29.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那是血液中毒 败血病\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That's blood poisoning. Septicemia.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.93,1:30:32.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她可能因败血产生休克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She could go into septic shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.23,1:30:34.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我以前见过 那可能很糟\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've seen that before. That can get bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.50,1:30:36.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}她需要大剂量的盘尼西林\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}She needs a massive dose of penicillin...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.70,1:30:40.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}或者立即使用广谱抗生素 不然...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...or a broad-spectrum antibiotic immediately, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.08,1:30:47.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不然什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.50,1:31:09.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我从来没见过这样的情形\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.00,1:31:13.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}没有参照点 我看到的全是云层\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}There's no point of reference. All I can see is cloud cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.81,1:31:15.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在干什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.48,1:31:17.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}拍摄红外线大气环流照片\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Taking infrared image of thermal currents.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.98,1:31:22.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}发到休斯顿 克罗勒夫 你的天气服务站\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Send to Houston, Korolev, your weather service.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.88,1:31:24.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我来帮你\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.55,1:31:27.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}汤姆？汤姆 起来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Tom? Tom, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.15,1:31:32.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我刚刚收到从航天站发来的卫星照片 你最好看一看\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I just received some satellite images from the space station. You better take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.07,1:31:45.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这个东西有多大？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How big is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.77,1:31:47.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}中心直径为五十英里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The vortex is 50 miles in diameter.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.97,1:31:51.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}还在增大 两个在欧洲和亚洲的云团甚至更大\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And growing. The two cells over Europe and Asia are even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.81,1:31:53.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}天啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Good God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.28,1:31:56.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这个将在一小时内袭击纽约\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}This one's gonna hit New York inside an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.70,1:32:14.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}詹森！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jason!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.37,1:32:15.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你还好吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.47,1:32:18.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}詹森！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jason!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.22,1:32:37.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你在干什么？- 那船上一定有药\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing? There's gotta be medicine on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.06,1:32:41.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我记得你说过外面太危险了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I thought you said it was too dangerous to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.39,1:32:42.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我知道我说过\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I know I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.04,1:32:51.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在哪里找到那些椅子的？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Where did you find those chairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.77,1:32:54.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}怎么了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.01,1:32:56.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我和你一起去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.04,1:32:59.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我也去\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.01,1:34:04.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来啊 该死的！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.59,1:34:56.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这都是俄文 我...我知道\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It's all in Russian. I...I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.43,1:34:59.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 嘿 伙计们 我找到了 - 什么？你怎么知道？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Hey, hey, hey, guys. I found it. - What? How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.17,1:35:02.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}因为瓶子上面写着“盘尼西林”\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Because it says "penicillin" on the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.84,1:35:09.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}嘿 等等 这是食堂\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Hey, wait. This is the mess hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.71,1:35:12.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 我们应该能找到些食品 - 我们没有时间了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- We should find some food. - We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.24,1:35:16.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}听着 没有食品我们不会坚持很久 包括劳拉\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Listen, none of us are gonna survive much longer without food. Including Laura.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.52,1:35:18.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好吧\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.69,1:35:26.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 萨姆 这里 - 什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- Sam, over here. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.83,1:35:28.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}中奖了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.57,1:35:41.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}布莱恩？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Brian?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.91,1:35:44.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我还好 发生什么了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm okay. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.61,1:35:47.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我只是打开了橱柜\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All I did was open up the cupboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.55,1:35:51.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们可以利用这个把食品放在里面\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, we can use it. Put food in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.93,1:36:05.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}拉他进来 布莱恩！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Pull him in, Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.47,1:36:11.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 你还好吗？- 天啊 还有很多狼\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- You all right? - Oh, my God, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.01,1:36:15.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我的腿\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}My leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.65,1:36:21.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 用这个\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Here, use this.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.22,1:36:31.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这个现在应该到达纽约了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It should be over New York by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.06,1:36:36.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}卫星显示每秒钟降低十度\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Satellite readings are showing a temperature drop of 10 degrees per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.14,1:36:53.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}伙计们...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.71,1:36:55.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我认为我们处在风眼了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...I think we're in the eye of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.88,1:36:58.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们现在必须要回去了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We gotta get back right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.15,1:37:04.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}听着 我会去外面 我来引诱狼群离开房间\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Look, I'm gonna go outside, and I'm gonna lure the wolves out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.46,1:37:06.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}当他们离开的时候 你们锁上门\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}When they leave, you lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.36,1:37:08.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}祝你好运\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.56,1:38:17.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}布莱恩 快点 我需要点东西\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Brian, hurry. I need something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.90,1:38:19.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 快点！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.61,1:38:31.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}布莱恩！布莱恩 打开门！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Brian! Brian, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.55,1:38:38.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们现在必须走\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We have to get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.58,1:38:40.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}布莱恩 带上给养\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Brian, get the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.24,1:39:39.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}糟糕 快走！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Oh, shit. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.71,1:39:41.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}拉 布莱恩！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Pull, Brian!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.02,1:40:20.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}把药给劳拉\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Take the medicine to Laura.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.62,1:40:54.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们快到了 来！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're almost there. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.65,1:40:58.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}布莱恩！关上门！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Brian! Close the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.70,1:41:12.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不要让火熄灭！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Don't let the fire go out!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.20,1:41:13.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}发生了什么事？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.68,1:41:23.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}狗狗 离门远点\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Buddha, come away from the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.55,1:41:25.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}来 狗狗 来！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Come, Buddha, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.92,1:41:28.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}快烧书！快烧书！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}More books! More books!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.14,1:42:24.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我昏了多久了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How long have I been out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.44,1:42:27.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}几个小时\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Couple hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.31,1:42:28.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你感觉如何？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.01,1:42:31.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}好 发生什么了？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Okay. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.02,1:42:36.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们进来的时候太急了 所以我推了你一把\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Well, we had to get inside in kind of a hurry, so I sort of pushed you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.86,1:42:39.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我应该适应你这么推我的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I should be used to you pushing me around.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.46,1:42:43.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你醒过来太好了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Good to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.73,1:42:50.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你在干什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.60,1:42:55.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}风眼已经过去了 我们离曼哈顿还有四十英里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The eye of the storm has passed, and we're 40 miles from Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.94,1:42:57.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们是不是该多等一天？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Shouldn't we wait one more day?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.45,1:43:03.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}萨姆也许挺不了这一天\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sam may not have one more day.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.09,1:44:17.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你觉得我们会怎么样？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What do you think's gonna happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.99,1:44:19.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你指什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.06,1:44:25.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我是说我们 文明 每个人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I mean us. Civilization. Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.77,1:44:30.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}人类渡过了上个冰川时期\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mankind survived the last Ice Age.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.04,1:44:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们当然有能力渡过这一次\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're certainly capable of surviving this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.64,1:44:39.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}一切取决于我们是否能从我们的错误中吸取教训\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}All depends on whether or not we're able to learn from our mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.71,1:44:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我是肯定会从我的错误中吸取教训\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I sure as hell would like a chance to learn from mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.12,1:44:48.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你已经尽力而为了啊\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You did everything you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.49,1:44:53.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我是说萨姆\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I was thinking about Sam.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.57,1:45:02.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克 你知道萨姆活下来的可能性...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack, you know the chances of Sam...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.08,1:45:16.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我对我儿子承诺过\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I made my son a promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.78,1:45:19.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我会遵守诺言的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm going to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.31,1:45:46.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}帕克 这里是休斯顿 你听到了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Parker, this is Houston. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.45,1:45:48.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}收到 控制中心 继续\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Roger, mission control. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.58,1:45:52.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们收到零星的报道显示风暴正在北美消失\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We've got scattered reports that the storm is dissipating over North America.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.88,1:45:54.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你可以确认这一点吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Can you confirm?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.19,1:45:59.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}的确如此 终于开始消散了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Affirmative. It's finally clearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.36,1:46:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们现在在欧洲上空\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We're over Europe right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.09,1:46:05.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我近几天来第一次看到地表\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I can see landmass for the first time in days.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.47,1:47:57.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}离图书馆还有多远？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}How much further is it to the library?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.11,1:47:59.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}应该...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}It should be...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.75,1:48:04.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}就在这里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.82,1:48:10.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}对不起 杰克\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I'm sorry, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.63,1:48:50.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}萨姆？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.66,1:50:01.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那是谁？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.14,1:50:09.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我父亲\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}My father.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.88,1:50:15.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你做到了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}You made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.68,1:50:21.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我当然会做到的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.95,1:50:53.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}美国大使馆\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}EMBASSY OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.54,1:51:14.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}总统先生\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.51,1:51:19.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我收到了来自杰克·霍尔的短波信息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've just received a shortwave radio transmission from Jack Hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.05,1:51:22.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他到了纽约\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He made it to New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.81,1:51:24.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}他说那里有幸存者\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}He says there are survivors.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.42,1:51:28.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}谢谢 汤姆\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Thank you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.19,1:51:30.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那是...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.76,1:51:33.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}那是好消息\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}That's good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.00,1:51:48.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}过去的几个星期里让我们感到在大自然的力量面前\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}These past few weeks have left us all with a profound sense of humility...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.24,1:51:51.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们是多么的渺小\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...in the face of nature's destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.68,1:51:55.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}多年来 我们一直以为我们可以...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}For years, we operated under the belief that we could continue...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.55,1:52:01.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不记后果地挥霍我们星球的自然资源\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...consuming our planet's natural resources without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.12,1:52:03.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们错了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.29,1:52:07.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我错了\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.06,1:52:12.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}实际上我的首次致辞是在外国的土地上 大使馆里发表的\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}The fact that my first address to you comes from a consulate on foreign soil...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.63,1:52:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}这为我们证明了世界的改变\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...is a testament to our changed reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.30,1:52:18.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}不只是美国人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Not only Americans...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.37,1:52:21.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}地球上所有的人现在都成为了被我们称之为...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...but people all around the globe are now guests in the nations...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.94,1:52:24.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}第三世界的国家的客人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...we once called The Third World.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.91,1:52:29.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在我们需要的时候 他们接纳和收容了我们\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}In our time of need, they have taken us in and sheltered us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.88,1:52:33.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我对他们的好客深表感谢\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}And I am deeply grateful for their hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.01,1:52:59.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我们悼念那位逝世的领导人 他英勇的发布了疏散命令\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}We mourn the loss of a spirited leader whose courageous order to evacuate...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.34,1:53:04.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}彼得？嘿 你今天感觉好点了吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Peter? Hey, you feeling okay today?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.25,1:53:07.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}数天之中 我们对那些被困在北部人们的...\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}For days, we've despaired about the fate of the people...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.29,1:53:09.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}命运失去了信心\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...who are trapped in the North.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.79,1:53:13.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}今天 出现了一线希望\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Today, there is cause for hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.36,1:53:17.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在几小时前 我收到了消息 一小队人\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Only a few hours ago, I received word that a small group of people...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.10,1:53:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在几乎不可能的情况下克服了巨大的困难\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...survived in New York City against all odds...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.57,1:53:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}在纽约市幸存了下来\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...and in the face of tremendous adversity.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.57,1:53:27.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}我命令一个紧急搜寻和救助小队\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}I've ordered an immediate search-and-rescue mission...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.44,1:53:31.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}立刻把他们带回来 并且寻找其它的幸存者\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}...to bring them home and to look for more survivors.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.14,1:54:03.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}杰克！\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.11,1:54:07.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}- 见到你真是太高兴了 - 来 咱们上飞机\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}- It's good to see you. - Come on, let's go get on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.93,1:55:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}看看那里\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.24,1:55:06.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}什么？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.84,1:55:10.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24\bord1\shad0\1c&HEBEBEB&\b0}你见过这么清澈的天空吗？\N{\fnTahoma\fs16\bord1\shad0\1c&H0084FF&\b0}Have you ever seen the air so clear?


